{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/day2/","result":{"data":{"site":{"id":"Site","siteMetadata":{"title":"Rafał Moneta"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"51266f04-f8b6-5505-b12d-4cab7d2570e8","excerpt":"On day 2, I decided to publish some code on GitHub. To do that, I had to learn how to hide your API keys. There is a simple guide on how to do that. How to hide…","html":"<p>On day 2, I decided to publish some code on GitHub. To do that, I had to learn how to hide your API keys. There is a simple guide on how to do that.</p>\n<h2>How to hide sensitive data in .env file</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a file called .env in the root of your project’s directory.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 197px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/22326df0bf50ccc1303cbc720b03a27b/1c154/directory.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 113.19796954314721%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"directory\"\n        title=\"directory\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/22326df0bf50ccc1303cbc720b03a27b/1c154/directory.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/22326df0bf50ccc1303cbc720b03a27b/1c154/directory.png 197w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 197px) 100vw, 197px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>Inside the .env file create name to your API key, for example <strong>REACT<em>APP</em>MOVIEDB_KEY</strong> and add .env file to .gitignore.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 900px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/2ff52a8b15e901550da4b8929aa1bee3/e405b/envfile.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36.65389527458493%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"env and gitignore\"\n        title=\"env and gitignore\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/2ff52a8b15e901550da4b8929aa1bee3/1cfc2/envfile.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/2ff52a8b15e901550da4b8929aa1bee3/3684f/envfile.png 225w,\n/blog/static/2ff52a8b15e901550da4b8929aa1bee3/fc2a6/envfile.png 450w,\n/blog/static/2ff52a8b15e901550da4b8929aa1bee3/1cfc2/envfile.png 900w,\n/blog/static/2ff52a8b15e901550da4b8929aa1bee3/21482/envfile.png 1350w,\n/blog/static/2ff52a8b15e901550da4b8929aa1bee3/e405b/envfile.png 1566w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>\n<p>Access the API key via the process.env object.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">process</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">env</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">REACT_APP_MOVIEDB_KEY</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>If after saving files and reloading the page this do not work, try to restart your server!</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  :root {\n    --grvsc-padding-v: 1rem;\n    --grvsc-padding-h: 1.5rem;\n    --grvsc-padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-v);\n    --grvsc-padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-h);\n    --grvsc-padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-v);\n    --grvsc-padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-h);\n    --grvsc-border-radius: 8px;\n  \n    --grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color: transparent;\n    --grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width: 4px;\n    --grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color: transparent;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top);\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom);\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: inline-block;\n    min-width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: inline-block;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left);\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-highlighted {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color);\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color);\n  }\n  \n  .dark-default-dark {\n    background-color: #1E1E1E;\n    color: #D4D4D4;\n  }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk10 { color: #4EC9B0; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk1 { color: #D4D4D4; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk11 { color: #DCDCAA; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk12 { color: #9CDCFE; }\n</style>","frontmatter":{"title":"Day 2 - How to hide your API keys and sensitive data","date":"February 11, 2020","description":"Simple guide on how to hide your sensitive data","time":2}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/day2/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/day1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Day 1 - How to fetch data from a few APIs"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/day3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Day 3 to 6 - My react movie-app"}}}}}